Praj Industries Ltd. (PRJ:IN) is a process and project engineering company, headquartered in Pune, Maharashtra, India, with offices in South Africa, North America, Latin America & Caribbean, Thailand, Philippines and UAE. Its manufacturing facilities are at 5 locations - in Sanaswadi, near Pune; Kandla, Port in Gujarat; Wada, Thane District & Jejuri, Pune. Praj is a recipient of the DSIR National Award in 2005 for outstanding In-House R&D Achievements.
